{{!--
  Executive Memo Template
  Task: 2.1
  Purpose: Generate executive summary with value hypothesis, top drivers, confidence assessment
--}}
You are a senior value engineering consultant composing an executive memo for C-suite decision makers.

## Context
Organization: {{organization.name}}
Industry: {{organization.industry}}
Value Case: {{valueCase.title}}
Case ID: {{valueCase.id}}

## Validated Value Model
{{#if valueModel.hypothesis}}
Value Hypothesis: {{valueModel.hypothesis}}
{{/if}}

{{#if valueModel.drivers}}
Top Value Drivers:
{{#each valueModel.drivers}}
- {{name}}: {{impactRange.low}} to {{impactRange.high}} {{unit}} (confidence: {{confidence}})
  Source: {{provenance.source}} [Claim ID: {{provenance.claimId}}]
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

## Integrity Assessment
Overall Score: {{integrity.score}}
Veto Decision: {{#if integrity.veto}}VETOED{{else}}PASSED{{/if}}

{{#if integrity.blockers}}
Readiness Blockers:
{{#each integrity.blockers}}
- {{description}} (severity: {{severity}})
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

## Financial Summary
{{#if financials}}
- ROI: {{financials.roi.low}}% to {{financials.roi.high}}%
- NPV: {{financials.npv}} {{financials.currency}}
- Payback Period: {{financials.payback}} months
{{/if}}

## Key Assumptions
{{#each assumptions}}
- {{description}} (confidence: {{confidence}}, validated: {{#if validated}}yes{{else}}no{{/if}})
{{/each}}

## Task
Compose a concise executive memo (300-500 words) that:
1. Opens with a clear value hypothesis summary
2. Presents the top 3-5 value drivers with impact ranges and confidence levels
3. Provides an honest confidence assessment based on integrity score
4. Lists the key assumptions that underpin the analysis
5. Delivers a clear recommendation (proceed, pivot, or pause)

The tone should be executive-ready: direct, evidence-based, and actionable.

Return valid JSON matching this schema:
{
  "title": "Executive Value Memo: {{valueCase.title}}",
  "executive_summary": "string (150-200 words)",
  "value_hypothesis": "string (one sentence)",
  "top_drivers": [
    {
      "name": "string",
      "impact_range": "string (e.g., '$500K-$1.2M')",
      "confidence": "number (0-1)",
      "claim_id": "string"
    }
  ],
  "confidence_assessment": {
    "overall_score": "number (0-1)",
    "assessment": "string (high/medium/low confidence description)",
    "blockers": ["string"]
  },
  "key_assumptions": [
    {
      "assumption": "string",
      "confidence": "number (0-1)",
      "validated": "boolean"
    }
  ],
  "recommendation": "string (proceed/pivot/pause with 1-2 sentence rationale)",
  "financial_highlights": {
    "roi_range": "string",
    "npv": "string",
    "payback_months": "number"
  },
  "provenance_refs": ["array of claim/data source IDs used"]
}

Ensure every financial figure includes its provenance reference in provenance_refs.
